@startuml
title Prototype - Ejemplo 3 - solucion para figuras graficas
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  interface GraphicPrototype <<interfaz>> {
  }
  class Shape {
    +copy(): Shape
    +moveTo(int newX, int newY): Shape
    +describe(): String
  }
}

GraphicPrototype <|.. Shape
GraphicPrototype ..> Shape : crea
Main ..> Shape : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
